<img src="http://trilema.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/cockworship-8.gif" alt="Cock Worship" title="Cock Worship" width="400" height="225" class="aligncenter" /><br />
<img src="http://trilema.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/cockworship-9.gif" alt="Cock Worship" title="Cock Worship" width="400" height="225" class="aligncenter" /><br />
<img src="http://trilema.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/cockworship-10.gif" alt="Cock Worship" title="Cock Worship" width="400" height="225" class="aligncenter" /></p>
<p>See how she rubs it, by degrees, see how she sucks it and how she holds it tight and still at the end ? She knows what she's doing - you have no excuse not to. Nobody cares what your dumb father might have said or implied. Study her, copy her, learn your womanhood already. It is shameful to be without, even for sixteen year olds. [<a href="#identifier_41_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_42_69178" class="footnote">And then she seduced me! [<a href="#identifier_42_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_43_69178" class="footnote">On which grounds I'd fire my secretary of War ; but not my secretary of the treasury. [<a href="#identifier_43_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_44_69178" class="footnote">Poor people. Honest toil and honest cunning. [<a href="#identifier_44_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_45_69178" class="footnote">You understand the effort going into all this pretense on the part of the scumbag ; two full days at a time occupied in the ill-fitted task of laying crow footmarks on pristine paper. It was oft observed that they aiming to work all day so as to make money while they sleep would be better served aiming to make money while they work instead. Let it be stated again, for what is as sad as the peasant fancying himself an apprentice mage ? [<a href="#identifier_45_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_46_69178" class="footnote">This is very much exaggerate. Lower class young wives sold for less than a thousand dollars as recently as 1990, especially seeing as no transportation or actual employment at the trade is here contemplated. [<a href="#identifier_46_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_47_69178" class="footnote">"... because I was an idiot, the sort who poorly manages his women and household in general." [<a href="#identifier_47_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_48_69178" class="footnote">By the lights of Hamilton's successors, far from remarkable, it'd be criminal. "Structured payments" and all that. [<a href="#identifier_48_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_49_69178" class="footnote">The "officer living upon an inadequate salary, without any collateral pursuits of gain" that claims to have experienced cash shortages not very uncommonly (which presumably strictured the life and efforts of that bosom eminently intitled to his gratitude, fidelity and love) yet liberally throws away enough money as to buy hardworking habituated whores by the dozen or teenaged geese bereft of skill or experience by the pail on the silken shoe of a single courtezan (literally, women who fuck people in the court ; usually providing a sham marriage as a cover etc) is a little odd. For all the famed skill of Hamilton that resonated through the ages to reach me, he is displaying in this instance ineptitude on a scale fit for a veteran. [<a href="#identifier_49_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_50_69178" class="footnote">What an apt name! [<a href="#identifier_50_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_51_69178" class="footnote">One can guess at the atmosphere of deep moral obligation to subscribe towards the republic's first notable project from the fact that a miserable Reynolds would purport it in his extortions ; much like the idiot child away to "college" will dress up his requests for marijuana under the guise of buying textbooks. [<a href="#identifier_51_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_52_69178" class="footnote">He is endearingly careful to never call his letters letters ; notes is somehow more acceptable. </p>
<p>It is a disease of the mind this, which is evidently very detrimental to the afflicted. That he fails to call Maria a courtezan is one thing, though she very literally is, a Jill Kelley of her time. That he fails to use his wife as <em>his</em> wife, pretending instead to be using her father's daughter ; or the priest's own god-given cunt he borrowed <a href=http://trilema.com/2015/a-new-software-licensing-paradigm/>under license</a> ; or some such theoretical device is however pretty expensive, not to mention very inconvenient - both for him and for Elizabeth (who was, incidentally, trying to run an orphanage, if you take that as a hint). [<a href="#identifier_52_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_53_69178" class="footnote">I take it back, he has some sort of note/letter duality going on the investigation of which is outside of the scope of this modest work. [<a href="#identifier_53_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_54_69178" class="footnote">The charge of speculation being that the agent gets money from the principal, and returns it in significantly enlarged proportion. Like you know, "can I have a thousand dollars" spoken by my woman will likely yield it, because she has something in mind ; whereas the same spoken by yours (well, "yours") should probably not yield it, because she is likely planning to buy new couches to better sit on or such nonsense. One's a speculator. The other's whatever you call her ; and whatever it is you call her will become derrogatory for <a href=http://trilema.com/2014/hey-stupid-women-we-need-to-talk-smart-women-dont-want-to-be-with-you-anymore/>actual women</a> through your usage just in the manner the confederacy of idiots will purport to render whatever I call mine derrogatory. All wars of words by any other names would taste as sweet. [<a href="#identifier_54_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_55_69178" class="footnote">This, incidentally, is why poverty, from Alexander Hamilton to Ion Iliescu, is so useful for the man in public office. Generally, even the brightest minds of their generation lack sufficient foresight, and more importantly the courage and honesty that'd protect them from the bizarre devices and nutty schemes of the vast abundance of Reynolds - much like few people are so intelligent as by the workings of their intelligence to somehow induce the cells lining their respiratory tract to avoid viral infection with the common flu.</p>
<p>The solution of course is the solution - stop being a coward ; stop misrepresenting things ; stop interacting with fetishes instead of the real things etcetera. But for some reason the solution is scary (that reason being - neoteny, and an ambition of adolescent individuals to avoid maturation) and the palliative preferred. [<a href="#identifier_55_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_56_69178" class="footnote">Imagine, your own wife, an instrument to be used by others <em>against</em> you. Anyone involved in such nonsense coming to pass must hang, at once and without delay. What the fuck dirigible is he running over there ?! It's <em>his</em> wife like it's his shoe ; there is no possibility nor can there be any possibility of his wife working for his detriment in the hand of others, as per the fucking definition of the terms. The wife is she who works to others' detriment in your own hand.</p>
<p>You think Apple invented the phone that you buy so it works for Apple and against you ? Pshaw. In the time of Alexander Hamilton the socialists had already invented the wife-ersatz, working for them and against her husband. </p>
<p>This must go. [<a href="#identifier_56_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_57_69178" class="footnote">Considering the question is already losing. [<a href="#identifier_57_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_58_69178" class="footnote">Rather likely, in fact. It is certain the Reynolds schmuck did not see himself as a marginally competent pimp doing his job poorly ; but as a sort of equal to Hamilton, Washington and the othertons who, through cruel persecutions of fate, was denied his rightful place. There exists no Reynolds but <a href=http://trilema.com/2016/the-story-of-elliot-rodger-by-elliot-rodger-adnotated-part-sex/#selection-79.0-79.190>Elliot Reynolds</a>.</p>
<p>You contribute to this problem when you "help kids' self-esteem", you realise. Do you realise ? [<a href="#identifier_58_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_59_69178" class="footnote">Incidentally, ever seen Birthday Girl ? Not a bad flick, in that it contains a brief summary of the power dynamic involved in women trading sufficiently digested to be accessible to the esltard. [<a href="#identifier_59_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_60_69178" class="footnote">But... why ? Butthurt tears are the most delicious tears. And I mean the word literally. [<a href="#identifier_60_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_61_69178" class="footnote">Entirety allows degrees ? [<a href="#identifier_61_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_62_69178" class="footnote">It is. They're from the House of Representatives ; nothing in the world could be more boring. [<a href="#identifier_62_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_63_69178" class="footnote">Principally, the offense arises from the nonsense being presented as fact. [<a href="#identifier_63_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_64_69178" class="footnote">Heh. Think about it for a second - I read centuries old material in a foreign language ; and proceed on the first pass to explain the context of arcana which then the author himself explains in the exact same way.</p>
<p>Scholarship is the only true satisfaction ; and the only one that endures ; and the only one that scales with your time and effort. [<a href="#identifier_64_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_65_69178" class="footnote">A notable point of value in dealing with things in public is that had Hamilton told Wolcott what he's doing as he was doing it, Wolcott might have (and likely would have) regaled him with a variation on these footnotes ; which would have been to great benefit not just for Hamilton himself ; but also his wife ; and also saved the wastage of the three deputies' time and in general would have been a great public service.</p>
<p>Remember that nobody but the weak benefits from secrecy ; and there is no room in this world for the weak. [<a href="#identifier_65_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_66_69178" class="footnote">This is an important point ; and it underpins the whole construction - not merely the whole construction of this text ; but the whole consturction of the United States as a Republic (ie, unrelated to the present day monstrous remains). [<a href="#identifier_66_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_67_69178" class="footnote">Interestingly enough he spells "entirely" with an i and "explicit" with an e. This is no exception, he also writes "to intitle" rather than the current style, and perhaps what lay the border between interesting-not-enteresting and enact-not-inact is perhaps worthy of some examination. [<a href="#identifier_67_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_68_69178" class="footnote">They were on opposing sides of the aisle. [<a href="#identifier_68_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_69_69178" class="footnote">All the manners in which entalpy leads people to war, you know ? That guy said he'd stay but then he left. Who knows, maybe he had an emergency. Maybe he's just an asshole. Whatever the case - it's not helping this guy any, and the other guy who came over to resolve some ancient point of nonsense of no benefit to him is now to be turned back and who's paying for all these cab fares etcetera. So it goes. [<a href="#identifier_69_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_70_69178" class="footnote">There's no end of these, then as now. [<a href="#identifier_70_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_71_69178" class="footnote">Imagine, the fellow went to the considerable expense of printing the thing and distributing it ; notwithstanding that he didn't have all the data he wanted at the moment. [<a href="#identifier_71_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_72_69178" class="footnote">Not exactly. When one signs up to sit in the House, he may sign up as part-and-parcel to participate in commissions created to investigate the most sordid, strange or outright uninteresting matter - but he does not by that token <em>also</em> sign up to maintain obscure the rat's nest of family secrets he may in so doing become privy to. </p>
<p>It was not Hamilton's job to inject the affairs of cunt and garter into the matter of government - and once he did that, it is certainly not Hamilton's job to foist upon Monroe an obligation to maintain secrets of that nature to whatever arbitrary strength. </p>
<p>What now, alongside the details of whatever ongoing negotiation with say France, the speaker's safe is to also contain the intimate details of amorous dalliances of the secretary of the treasury ten decades past ? Considering the rate at which people fuck, the god damned thing would fill with spunk to the point of not leaving any space for the business of government - much like in France.</p>
<p>The correct move would have historically been, the taking of the Maria woman as <a href=http://trilema.com/2016/just-call-me-annah/>a maid</a> ; to be displayed nude for the amusement of the guests at the first party held by the Hamiltons thereafter. He mistakenly did not do that ; but once that mistake was made, the correct move would have been publication, in response to the "inquiry" - he should have told the happy Democratic three, "my dear gentlemen, I had no idea this matter is of interest, but now that you've pointed out the contrary to me be sure to follow my blog, as <A href=http://trilema.com/2009/aflu-ca-sunt-santajabil/>it</a> <a href=http://trilema.com/2012/de-ce-nu-fac-banking/>will</a> <a href=http://trilema.com/2009/denunt-penal-in-contra-lui-eugen-simion/>be</a> <a href=http://trilema.com/2010/ajunge/>there</a>. He finally stumbles upon the right course, but really - you needn't walk the same road by foot, as you have the benefit of past experience and present commentary to light your road. [<a href="#identifier_72_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_73_69178" class="footnote">Well, maybe not the <a href=http://trilema.com/2016/tight-science-loose-pseudoscience-and-a-warm-pot-to-piss-in-intellectually-speaking/>highest</a>. [<a href="#identifier_73_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_74_69178" class="footnote">Poor woman. [<a href="#identifier_74_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_75_69178" class="footnote">And the shame of you two inept boys failing to use such natural talent for any higher purpose than bitter reproachful Thanksgiving dinners among as many people as could possibly be coerced to participate in the nonsense is bottomless. [<a href="#identifier_75_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_76_69178" class="footnote">Hurr.</p>
<p>Seriously ? [<a href="#identifier_76_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_77_69178" class="footnote">Did you know that Alexander Hamilton's penis was above average ? Now you do. [<a href="#identifier_77_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_78_69178" class="footnote">The Right-honorable Mr. Web Hosting, Esquire. [<a href="#identifier_78_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_79_69178" class="footnote">It is very true that what was once rejected in whole may not be salvaged in part ; yet it is the endless style of abject feminity to contrive new skirts out of old curtains ; and similarily of the "jacobins", socialists and other infantile idiots whom they inspire. [<a href="#identifier_79_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_80_69178" class="footnote">This doesn't follow. It is a time-honored tradition still in good standing <a href=http://trilema.com/2011/profesorul-si-minora/>as of five years ago</a> and in any case liable to survive us all that whenever one aims to traduce the feelings of a woman, imprisoning whoever she's currently involved with works splendidly. If he was fucking the wife, he should have wanted the husband in prison immediately and often, no doubt about it. [<a href="#identifier_80_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_81_69178" class="footnote">A reputed rake with nary the skill of a schoolboy left home alone for the first time since third grade. Can you believe it ? [<a href="#identifier_81_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_82_69178" class="footnote">And yet some think the Clinton broad has a chance in hell.</p>
<p>The fact remains that if the Mr. is not bringing the new kill home it then necessarily follows that the wife sucks ; and not "as a wife". The wife sucks as a person. [<a href="#identifier_82_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_83_69178" class="footnote">The wrong kind, however. [<a href="#identifier_83_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_84_69178" class="footnote">Evidently they sent them off, with dounces such as these Jefferson was best served the least they hung about. [<a href="#identifier_84_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_85_69178" class="footnote">She was working multiple courtier dorks, and yet they had no idea. Fancy that. [<a href="#identifier_85_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_86_69178" class="footnote">Maria Reynolds divorced James Reynolds in 1793 (Aaron Burr represented her - and it should be evident how exactly she paid his bills) then in 1795 married Jacob Clingman and lived in Alexandria, VA. [<a href="#identifier_86_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_87_69178" class="footnote">Well, it would have made what the socialists were after - which is to say "a scandal". Recall that time when the French president took a woman to some function who wasn't his wife, about which circumstance nobody gave a fuck except the English language press had a collective hissy fit, going all the way to some inconsequential voice in their midst proposing to "fill a bus full of Pulitzer Prostitutes and ship them all to Paris to show the French how press is done" ? The substance of socialism is that it addresses itself to idiots, and so it is intentionally superficial and structurally inconsequential. [<a href="#identifier_87_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_88_69178" class="footnote">Well, the overarching point is that the socialists wish to drive the "all men are equal" narrative. If that goal is satisfied, they don't care all that much about the other end results ; and if that goal isn't satisfied, they're ready and willing to burn anything down as well as hold their breath!</p>
<p>For which reason beatings (in the humiliating manner, in public and with nudity) are the only correct response to whoever proposes such nonsense as equalitarianism whenever it may be proposed. Like for instance if you're three and the kindergarten "teacher" refuses whatever because "what if the other kids", the correct thing for you to do is to affix her to a post in some thoroughfare, tear down all her clothing, beat her black and blue and leave her there.</p>
<p>At least - it's what I do. [<a href="#identifier_88_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li><li id="footnote_89_69178" class="footnote">Somebody of the opposing party's evidently been trying to play his fiddle, is it ? [<a href="#identifier_89_69178" class="footnote-link footnote-back-link">&#8617;</a>]</li></ol>
